Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:06.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:27.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:34.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又做噩梦了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:43.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:45.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:48.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,当盲目的群羊所聚集的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:57.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,燃起熊熊火柱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是天崩之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:03.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:09.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:12.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道...卡思嘉出事了?
Comment: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:07.42,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/-------START-------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,冬之精灵 宛如雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻地从天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:18.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,像棉花般飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住一看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我抓到一个不得了的东西 里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖怪板栗仔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 长高一点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦 艾莉加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,健壮了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:52.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差点没认出你来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,两年音讯全无呢 到底去了哪为何没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,先不叙旧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉她...没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉她不见了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎么回事 里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何会这样 什么时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我带了姐姐出去采集果实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个月前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为长期在矿洞生活 卡思嘉相当消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎都不怎么吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉加实在是看不下去就带她出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:50.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等我察觉到的时候 姐姐已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,里基特 那你为何还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不去找卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她什么情况你很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯你个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把姐姐丢在一边两年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:06.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己却不知死到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不懂里基特是什么心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他有去找过找了无数遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完全可以一去不回的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 里基特还是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有不能走的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得人睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:30.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,高特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,染上瘟疫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么高级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是天年 天年已到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:43.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 啰啰嗦嗦地问你话我也嫌麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看你的剑跟义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卷刃 生锈 变形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你在废寝忘食地斩妖除魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疯狂地厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不让自己神志清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,否则便活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:10.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,两年前 当里基特把身负重伤的你们带来这里时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:13.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你们身上发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但看到随后而来的那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总算可以想像并不是什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 报仇? 血债血偿?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不觉得这是在逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:29.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到报仇雪恨的战斗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨这种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:37.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法面对悲伤之人逃避的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:43.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇就如同将生锈的剑没在血泊中去磨锋利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越磨越生锈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越是生锈就越要磨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:52.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后只剩下一团锈粉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种舒适的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:07.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即将不留任何遗憾地逝去的你是不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有谁能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不剩地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何先兆地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:21.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,突如其来地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不讲理地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如同蝼蚁一般!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在一无所知的情形下!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间就...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心中 他们都是无可替代的存在!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:40.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但你却抛下那无可替代之人 独自离去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,两年前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:47.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你抛下那个从苦难中被救出来的最后一个无可替代之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,独自离去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你独自一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...逃进了用仇恨来燃烧自己的复仇行为中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:00.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抛下那位姑娘 独自离去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有资格说「为同伴报仇」这句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然跑去复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:17.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一柄出鞘的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有着无数卷刃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,血淋淋而快要生锈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有了致命龟裂...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...行将折断的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了让自己安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用我锻造的剑代替他们的墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也不是真的在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想必在数量上也差得很远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上经常这样干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,两年...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一段足以让人改变的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我深陷仇恨这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,里基特建立了剑冢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他接受了同伴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:06.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为之哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后找到新的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,凭着他独特的坚强意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使知道这里很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但黑暗中没有剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...我这辈子都不可能在夜晚安睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你独自离去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你独自一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:38.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...逃进了用仇恨来燃烧自己的复仇行为中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:53.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:10:01.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,烙在这右眼里最后的恐惧  憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:06.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这紫黑色的火焰绝对不能赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不能赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然无法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:13.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能让它燃烧自己 燃烧敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要继续浴血奋战!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,继续杀戮!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,继续嗜血!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独终老!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,永远!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抛下处于那种状况下的她独自离去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:36.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还能说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:40.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把等同鹰之团的卡思嘉抛在一边的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至没有资格说为同伴报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是前突击队长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道究竟是因为梦想或是其他原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总之他是为了自己而离开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们最艰难的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙 怎能让人将之称为同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经脱团了肥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有理由让你那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,带她走吧 即便是硬来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也一定要带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,否则那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要为自己奋战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:14.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,必须离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,独自一人也必须离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很早之前 从那时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我就没有那个资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我自己挑起的战争呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,确实这不是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:36.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少并没有为任何人所迫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己挑起的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:40.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:42.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些日子的篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还在燃烧着我的胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不正是这最后余下的细微篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:12.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后一刻阻止我被黑色火焰吞噬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...又重蹈覆辙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再失去她!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你不是睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我是睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我怕那样睡着的话会被吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:04.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:05.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆帮义肢加上钻头和切割机升级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这个太...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是鞋店小精灵而是铁匠小精灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:16.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 你那副样子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我必须要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太鲁莽了 让我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉加就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:28.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是我亲生女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:32.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是在战事中失去家人的战争孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:37.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她 只知道打铁的我才有个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:43.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 死的时候还是一个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...独自上路为好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别变成我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,新的铠甲如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:15.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是师傅帮你准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:21.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 使用了火药的新武器和新式改良弩炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不必特地组装也能马上在紧急光头使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近被称为圣地的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有什么头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里朝东北走三天左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个叫圣阿尔比安寺院的古修道院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人称判罪塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,判罪塔...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那里住满了难民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,据说似乎有邪教徒混在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以法王厅要派遣异端审问官过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,举行所谓的魔女审判
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但你为什么要问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:56.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为卡思嘉在那的可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有根据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可以说是溺水者的最后一根救命稻草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 现在只有相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:06.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不明白是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉是个什么样的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:15.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一定要平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,高特 你是个好铁匠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,归来之日再麻烦你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:28.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 不躺着可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕这次就是与你今生的永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 总比两眼泪汪汪地诀别要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,像那般朝着某个目标狂奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:47.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有路旁的风景被忽略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不如意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是生还是死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像是在民族大迁徙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瘟疫加饥荒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上库夏的大举入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听说首都温达姆在国王驾崩之际
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被人乘虚而入占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下任女王夏洛特公主以及以倚之为首的大部分家臣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,目前下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是屋漏偏逢连夜雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,注意言辞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,假若是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在要前往的阿尔比安修道院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是法王厅的直辖领地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但距离米特兰国境很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,库夏是我们教廷势力圈的共同敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是悠哉悠哉地进行异端审问仪式的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若有什么异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法王厅应该会传来新的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前我们只要默默完成任务就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:49.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人的心情比平常更糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没...没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要胡思乱想!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那不可能是真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会做出那种...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是幻觉 是噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要集中精神执行护送异端审问官的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便神明吝于在此身展示神迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要贯彻信仰就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:27.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你离神明十万八千里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是心情不好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不是我的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说可能有点过分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:43.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对法尔纳塞团长而言黑色剑士的担子太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:48.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅以追究她责任的形式解除其缉捕黑色剑士的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:52.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且新的任务居然是护卫那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,心情当然不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的马车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 以为自己是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 别乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是异端审问官的马车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看 高高褂起的红色车轮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:12.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那相当于是「血圣书」摩兹古斯的旗号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:14.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个「血圣书」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:18.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...车轮碾刑 刺刑 水刑 火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个家伙判以极刑的少说也有500人以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在拷问过程中死掉的人 更是多达数倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,相当遭人恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敌袭?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧 摩兹古斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:38.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子的仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:39.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿的仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,纳命来!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被难民挡着过不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,两侧被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出来 摩兹古斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:09.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神尊崇沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:16.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩兹古斯大人 您不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,万分抱歉 是我们的疏忽 太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞团长 抬起头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:25.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神对神职人员是宽容的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:30.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反而是法王厅方面的人没有死伤真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是神的庇护啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您说的话实在是不敢担
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我们会更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 这些人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是贫僧的手下 专门负责拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,经过严格的锻镰和任务考验
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有钢铁般的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:49.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使得他们在任何时候能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是令人安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:58.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你们为何要袭击我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是复仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你烧死了我们全村的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,污蔑是我们村是邪教徒村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:09.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,贫僧只是遵从神的教旨做出公正判决
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是因为碰上饥荒 粮食见底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才申请暂时停止向寺院上交什一税
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们却单方面地...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天诛!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你会遭报应的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天诛...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天诛?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎容得你说天诛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的行止不端之徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身为向僧侣出手的叛教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然说什么天诛!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你们这群鼠辈?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在这片大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我们法王厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:46.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,决不允许任何个人或组织拥有神之代言人的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞团长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:54.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为 该对他们判以什么刑罚才合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妄图弑僧之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:01.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,通常判处火刑或车轮碾刑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:05.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是光荣的圣铁锁骑士团团长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是见多识广
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:11.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就在这里进行简单的判法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,判决如下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:16.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,判处所有被告车轮碾刑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:19.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:31.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:45.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:50.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:53.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别 你会被牵连的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 姑娘 你是他的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 她是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 小心把你也...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 原来是疯子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:06.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,给我走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊 请大发慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:10.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫露加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真是可怕的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令人作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看那种景象只会令人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:20.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.37,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,为我家人报仇
